### ======================================================
### RESERVAESTUDIO - SUBSCRIPTION CHECKOUT (CONTRATO)
### ======================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@checkoutId = ec28b545-9495-4a92-8b29-0fa4b9f02ee3
@ownerToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI3MTI1YzVhOC1jMWNlLTQyYTctYmQ2OC0yNjQ2OGFiZGFhOGQiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzUxNzQ0MzEsImV4cCI6MTc3NTc3OTIzMX0.qBRDAfN5esOoi8iK328tDWtoXUaAvGzX2P2Bp0DNj7o
@subscriberToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJiZmQyZjllMS0zZWQzLTRmNzQtOWNjZC1jZGUzNWE4ZDMyZjYiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzUxODgyNTMsImV4cCI6MTc3NTc5MzA1M30.5Th17znMGtlUKZR74UwPTG3FnsoarGyPgvfDnv4sSx8
@stripeSignature = REPLACE_STRIPE_SIGNATURE

### @name startCheckout
### ✅ Iniciar checkout (plano + domínio + pagamento) - requer auth
### domainType: SUBDOMAIN (grátis) ou CUSTOM_DOMAIN (próprio). Com SUBDOMAIN, subdomain (slug) é obrigatório no body OU studioSlug no perfil.
### studioName opcional se já no cadastro. CUSTOM_DOMAIN exige customDomain no body.
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/start
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planTier": "PROFESSIONAL",
  "billingCycle": "ANNUAL",
  "domainType": "SUBDOMAIN",
  "subdomain": "rock-valley",
  "paymentMethod": "CARD",
  "totalAmount": 1970
}

### ✅ Consultar status de checkout
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/{{checkoutId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}

### ✅ Criar sessão Stripe (Checkout hospedado) — resposta: stripe.url para abrir no navegador
### (Somente se checkout.platformPaymentProvider === STRIPE, ex.: env PLATFORM_SUBSCRIPTION_PROVIDER=stripe)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/{{checkoutId}}/stripe/session
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}

### ✅ Mercado Pago — preapproval (cartão, etapa 1) — checkout.platformPaymentProvider === MERCADOPAGO
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/{{checkoutId}}/mercadopago/preapproval
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}

### ✅ Mercado Pago — anexar token de cartão (etapa 2)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/{{checkoutId}}/mercadopago/preapproval/card
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardTokenId": "REPLACE_MP_CARD_TOKEN"
}

### ✅ Mercado Pago — PIX / boleto (pagamento transparente)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/{{checkoutId}}/mercadopago/transparent-payment
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payerIdentificationType": "CPF",
  "payerIdentificationNumber": "12345678909"
}

### ✅ Webhook Stripe (payload assinado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/stripe/webhook
stripe-signature: {{stripeSignature}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "evt_test_webhook",
  "type": "checkout.session.completed",
  "data": {
    "object": {
      "object": "checkout.session",
      "id": "cs_test_123",
      "client_reference_id": "{{checkoutId}}",
      "metadata": {
        "checkoutId": "{{checkoutId}}"
      }
    }
  }
}

### ✅ Aprovar checkout (V1 manual por OWNER)
### @name approveCheckout
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/{{checkoutId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentReference": "evt_payment_ok_123"
}

### ✅ Adicionar sala via Settings (assinante USER vinculado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/studios/{{approveCheckout.response.body.checkout.studioId}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sala A - Ensaio",
  "type": "rehearsal",
  "description": "Ideal para bandas e ensaios.",
  "pricePerHour": 80,
  "capacity": 6,
  "features": ["Bateria acústica", "PA 1000W"]
}

### ❌ Approve sem token OWNER (deve retornar 401/403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/{{checkoutId}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentReference": "evt_payment_without_owner"
}

### ❌ Subdomínio indisponível (deve retornar 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/start
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planTier": "STARTER",
  "billingCycle": "MONTHLY",
  "studioName": "Outro Studio",
  "domainType": "SUBDOMAIN",
  "subdomain": "rock-valley",
  "paymentMethod": "PIX",
  "totalAmount": 80
}

### ❌ Webhook sem assinatura (deve retornar 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/stripe/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "evt_test_missing_signature"
}
